<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>HLA THAR SAKNAK CH451</title>
<key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh hmai ah mi tampi an i pum i A min thang-thatnak hla an sa,
 tingtang an tum.

[C1]
   Bawipa nih an dawt i sualnak an thlahpiak cang, A min thangtha
   zungzal seh, tiah an au cio ko.

[V2]
 Sualnak a ngeimi kha mi run hmai ka ah Puan rang aih in a min
 thang-thatnak hla an sa.

[C2]
   Bawipa nih an dawt i sualnak an thlahpiak cang, A min thangtha
   zungzal seh, tiah an au cio ko.

[V3]
 A hmemi kha a ngan bik ah a ser cang, A thi in a tawl cang, hla thar
 kha an sa cang.

[C3]
   Bawipa nih an dawt i sualnak an thlahpiak cang, A min thangtha
   zungzal seh, tiah an au cio ko.

[V4]
 Kan Bawipa a daw lo i a lei mi nih Sual thlahnak khamhnak bochan nak
 an hmu lai lo.

[C4]
   Bawipa nih an dawt i sualnak an thlahpiak cang, A min thangtha
   zungzal seh, tiah an au cio ko.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>451</hymn_number>
</song>